snippet.title: The Bunny Graveyard - Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
The first ever trailer for The Bunny Graveyard! This trailer was made very early in development, so a lot of things might change in the future! 

IMPORTANT NOTE: The November date at the end means November 2021, this date later got changed to September 22, 2023, which is when Chapter 1 officially released!

🐰WISHLIST ON STEAM 🐰
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1892420/The_Bunny_Graveyard/

🐦FOLLOW PICHON GAMES 🐦
https://twitter.com/pichongames

ABOUT
The Bunny Graveyard is an episodic horror adventure about a bunny who seeks to find the horrifying truth behind her existence. Immerse yourself in a world of pixel art inspired by GBA and NDS graphics, while unraveling an enthralling story that keeps you hooked!
